  "text": "Safety analysis of employing CPDLC for unmanned systems has been studied in [CITATION_1] . A faulty communication model has been tried out to examine the risks associated with the interference in CPDLC communications. However, as they assert the results, it is practical to use CPDLC in the UAS communication, but some adaptation is necessary to guarantee the message's integrity.",
